{"tid":1286674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"切 勿 被 大 中 華 膠 趁 火 打 劫","createTime":"2019-07-05T02:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T06:26:13.000Z","uid":37396,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62e68bbf038fed440ecaae51e9d6da7921211ad4","tid":1286674,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"自己香港啲野都未顧得掂你叫人去理大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我理撚得你支那亂七八糟都唔關我地事（當然如果佢越亂就越好）<br />\n佢地唔係反中共，係反焚化爐咋<br />\n你幫佢地佢地唔會感謝你，只會話你係港獨份子<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地只需focus 五大訴求：<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"5b0102bfb4b601b18f6e540f188df01eec1f81fc","tid":1286674,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb6027e3f6af8ca52ccf82a1ba6a5f77cea60a37","tid":1286674,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<code>\n我冇嘢講 我要見律師 坐夠48小時</code>"},{"pid":"e5a46b98bc58690f5208512a2b12e1f6ec641883","tid":1286674,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k